00:46:16,440 --> 00:46:19,360
Some might think,
and pardon me for saying this,

515
00:46:19,440 --> 00:46:24,280
you are imprisoning her,
according to Buddhism.

516
00:46:24,360 --> 00:46:26,599
Imprisoning her soul.

517
00:46:26,679 --> 00:46:32,199
If they are just keeping her head
and don't cremate it with her body,

