00:46:43,960 --> 00:46:47,039
So, I accept that
I have not been able to let go.

522
00:46:48,519 --> 00:46:52,639
I don't care that people think
we cannot let go

523
00:46:52,719 --> 00:46:55,440
and that we still hold on to her.

524
00:46:56,119 --> 00:46:59,559
