00:50:02,840 --> 00:50:04,440
He will live like a novice monk.

564
00:50:08,360 --> 00:50:10,679
[Matrix] I'm hoping that, by ordaining,

565
00:50:11,519 --> 00:50:15,079
I will be able to send protection
to my sister in the afterlife.

566
00:50:16,239 --> 00:50:19,480
