that you will have luck,

569
00:50:36,280 --> 00:50:39,920
be rid of sadness,
of disease and depression.

570
00:50:40,000 --> 00:50:40,880
Okay?

571
00:50:52,960 --> 00:50:56,199
My dear son,

572
00:50:56,280 --> 00:51:01,079
I hope that you find happiness.

573
00:51:01,159 --> 00:51:04,199
I'm so proud to be your mother.

574
00:51:28,320 --> 00:51:32,679
[Phra] When we lose, we weep.
