575
00:51:34,119 --> 00:51:36,920
Because we haven't accepted the truth.

576
00:51:37,599 --> 00:51:42,599
Our minds haven't opened wide enough
to accept the real truth.

577
00:51:45,039 --> 00:51:49,760
All life experiences
aging, suffering, and death.

