00:52:42,960 --> 00:52:44,920
I miss her crying.

588
00:52:45,880 --> 00:52:50,440
I miss the sound of her
calling our names. Calling my name.

589
00:52:52,880 --> 00:52:54,519
[monks chanting]

590
00:52:56,480 --> 00:53:02,000
Ordaining these two weeks means
