00:54:17,280 --> 00:54:20,360
Einz's repairs are about to be done.

600
00:54:22,519 --> 00:54:26,679
I walked over to her.

601
00:54:28,239 --> 00:54:29,960
And I asked the scientists,

602
00:54:32,400 --> 00:54:33,880
"Will she hear me, if I speak?"

603
00:54:35,599 --> 00:54:37,079
They told me,

604
00:54:38,840 --> 00:54:40,440
"She can sense that you are here."

605
00:54:41,639 --> 00:54:45,360
So I went over
and called her name, "My little Einz..."

606
00:54:46,559 --> 00:54:48,760
She moved a little.

607
00:54:50,599 --> 00:54:53,320
Then I had this feeling.

608
00:54:55,440 --> 00:54:56,440
This isn't real.

