00:56:44,920 --> 00:56:46,679
About her.

623
00:56:48,440 --> 00:56:53,000
Two years old,
with an older version of me.

624
00:56:53,079 --> 00:56:55,840
[chuckles] I don't even know,
50, 60 years old.

